            "title": "盤中速報 - 元山(6275)大漲8.04%，報55.1元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>元山(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6275:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6275\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6275-TW</a>)16日09:53股價上漲4.1元，報55.1元，漲幅8.04%，成交1,086張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>元山(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6275:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6275\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6275-TW</a>)所屬產業為電子零組件業，主要業務為電腦週邊設備。各式小家電。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲2.41%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.96%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+158 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+153 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+5 張</li> <li>融資增減：+31 張</li> <li>融券增減：-4 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
